   "name": "Scheduler Table Message Table",
   "description":  [
        "Steps to add a new message:",
        " 1. Add the topic to the 'topic-id-map' object. The entry must",
        "    be between the 'start' and 'end' entries and use the      ",
        "    following convention:      ",
        "     0 - cFE apps              ",
        "    10 - Base Camp runtime apps",
        "    20 - Dev & Demo apps       ",
        "    30 - User apps             ",
        " 2. Add a new 'message' object. N must be identical in ",
        "    topic-id-N must match",
        " 3. The sequence-segmentation flag entry 'seq-seg' can always",
        "    be set to 49152",
        "uint16  Sequence;     /* packet sequence word */                ",
        "  /*  bits  shift                description                  */",
        "  /* 0x3FFF    0  : sequence count                            */",
        "  /* 0xC000   14  : segmentation flags:  3 = complete packet  */",
        "uint16  Length;       /* packet length word */                  ",
        "  /*  bits  shift                description                  */",
        "  /* 0xFFFF    0  : (total packet length) - 7                 */"
        ],

   
